title: Week 9 preview & Falcons vs Buccaneers recap
itunes:title: Week 9 preview & Falcons vs Buccaneers recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game recapping each week 9 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Falcons and the Buccaneers.
